Puppet module: limits

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages limits software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include limits              # Install and run limits with standard configurations.
include limits::disable     # Disable limits service.
include limits::disableboot # Disable limits service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include limits::absent      # Remove limits package.

DEPENDENCIES:
